OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FLight
OL,6,Fand patchy rain spreading southeast on
OL,7,FSaturday morning, then mainly dry,
OL,8,Fbright and breezy. Mostly dry on
OL,9,FSunday, perhaps a few showers. Mostly
OL,10,Fdry on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
